        <li>IC/Passport: Clear, full-page photos (not cropped or blurry)</li>
        <li>Bank Statements: Full 6 months (not 3 months or bank book snapshots)</li>
        <li>SSM Registration: Current year Form 9/24/49 (not expired)</li>
        <li>Proof of Income: Contracts, invoices, or consistent bank deposits</li>
        <li>Lorry Details: Exact make, model, year, condition, asking price</li>
      </ul>

